<item>
            <title>[LU-11564] interop: sanity-hsm test 24g fails with &apos;hsm flags on /mnt/lustre/d24g.sanity-hsm/f24g.sanity-hsm are 0x00000009 != 0x0000000b&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11564</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test_24g started failing on October 16, 2018 with master tag 2.11.56.15 for interop testing only; master clients with 2.10.5 or 2.11.0 servers. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test was added for ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11369&quot; title=&quot;hsm: files are not dirtied when modified by someone else than their owner&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11369&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11369&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with patch with commit a9e48fa940 . &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test needs to be skipped for servers with version less than 2.11.56.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm tests 260a and 260b were also added for the same master tag and should be skipped. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Failures are at&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/9f9e6f86-d12e-11e8-ad90-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/9f9e6f86-d12e-11e8-ad90-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b2d8b53a-d6e1-11e8-82f2-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b2d8b53a-d6e1-11e8-82f2-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/70e20a04-d75f-11e8-b589-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/70e20a04-d75f-11e8-b589-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
